Package: regressr
Title: Minimal SHA Regression Testing Helpers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(person("Your", "Name", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides a helper to install two versions of a package from GitHub (identified by commit SHA) in isolated libraries and compare the results of a target function using waldo, suitable for use inside testthat tests and CI.
